longBusinessSummary: Taihan Cable & Solution Co., Ltd. designs, manufactures, and installs electric and communication cable systems worldwide. The company provides power generation and distribution cables, including extra-high voltage cables, overhead transmission lines, electric power cables, insulated wires, nuclear cables, halogen-free flame retardant cables, fire protection cables, control cables, instrumentation/signal cables, high voltage direct current cables, and subsea cables. It also offers communication, data, coaxial, railway signaling, optical, and UL style cables, as well as accessories; base metal products, such as copper rods and magnet wires; and heating systems, trolley wires, and factory automation cables. The company was formerly known as Taihan Electric Wire Co., Ltd. The company was founded in 1955 and is headquartered in Anyang, South Korea.
